{"tid":2393197,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"區諾軒大聲公襲警罪成上訴遭駁回 潘敏琦今頒判詞指行為懷惡意 明顯是情緒發洩 尊貴議員針對警察可見其不屑或貶意","createTime":"2021-02-03T09:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T14:11:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"540b3fde599f4b30e06527483d1cae4b6bf6c88a","tid":2393197,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:47:10.000Z","msg":"前立法會議員區諾軒前年7月到旺角調停警方清場，其間用咪高峰底敲鑿警員長盾，及後被指用大聲公近距離發言，損害警司高振邦的耳朵，受審後兩項襲警罪成。他早前向高等法院就定罪提上訴，即日遭法官潘敏琦駁回。潘官今頒下書面理據，指區諾軒當日阻撓清場行動，行為必屬非法，不斷追着警司用大聲公發言，亦屬有惡意。<br />\n<br />\n法官指出，現場有人大叫「人踩人」時，是否真的出現人踩人情況，不得而知；但區諾軒在有人叫「人踩人」之前，已辱罵警員「死黑警」及在前線叫嚷，阻撓清場行動及用大聲公鑿打警員的長盾。法官認為上訴方的人踩人論點屬事後孔明、擾亂視聽的砌詞。上訴人敲鑿警員長盾，明顯是發洩情緒，以當時情況，不可能屬可接受範圍及得到允許，行為屬非法。<br />\n<br />\n判決理由書重申法官早前在庭上說法，指區諾軒以尊貴議員身份，針對性地稱呼警察為「死黑警」及「毅進仔」，可見其不屑或貶意。法官自言並非活在象牙塔內，知道「毅進仔」一詞的由來或含意。上訴人說話帶有貶意和惡意，不言而喻。他向聽從指示執行職務的警員施壓、強人所難和肆意挑釁謾罵，上訴方指區不知警長不同意長盾被襲擊之說，不攻自破。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/33L5VTQQDRENFIMDJZZKLY6VFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2F33L5VTQQDRENFIMDJZZKLY6VFY%2F&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjVxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=268f05aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2F33L5VTQQDRENFIMDJZZKLY6VFY%2F&h=9800841f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/33L5VTQQDRENFIMDJZZKLY6VFY/</a>"},{"pid":"79eb384771a622c0d1896c1ab540cb64e7da5658","tid":2393197,"uid":26014,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:50:59.000Z","msg":"毅進仔係貶意法官大人都認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e82a31f6c5bfa4435d69a9c2228c6170ffb132","tid":2393197,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:51:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2391134/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2391134/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n大律師公會主席洋五毛夏博義話香港法官好專業,絕無司法迫害"},{"pid":"c22b3aca07641f62bbe14cef8e4b03a2d69b7e6a","tid":2393197,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19884ed4a862f4db3f35e9a4913f3d30967995e","tid":2393197,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"連個官都睇唔起毅進仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb06d39e6cc42ed591ce7e9e294d811b0fc136a","tid":2393197,"uid":231480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"又係潘書記"},{"pid":"9f776d48132a606a90b38fd19e90ff3188db3361","tid":2393197,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"社會服務令？"},{"pid":"4b1f138aa0bf363f78fcb0d786e5f3befb9086bd","tid":2393197,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b19884ed4a862f4db3f35e9a4913f3d30967995e","tid":2393197,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"連個官都睇唔起毅進仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:55:19.000Z","msg":"個上文下理係咁寫，我無老屈架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n針對性地稱呼警察為「死黑警」及<span class=\"x-large\">「毅進仔」</span>，可見其不屑或<span class=\"xx-large\">貶意</span>"},{"pid":"2ae7737adf5dcc7f0f33d2bd98ee8ba2cdc473e5","tid":2393197,"uid":335434,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-